## Welcome New Community Members
 Abigail Halder (AH), John Suykerbuyk (JS) introduced themselves.

## Meeting Minute Approval & Old Business
* Meeting minutes will be approved via GitHub. DM reviewed the old Business covered in the previous meeting. 

## Announcements
* SIG Repos
DM informed about the creation of two repositories under the governance organisation.  

* TAC Tech Talk Guidelines up (Thanks, Fritz!)
DM expressed gratitude to Fritz Alder for creating the TAC Tech Talk guidelines & which can be referred to in future. 
[TAC Talk Guidlines](https://github.com/confidential-computing/governance/blob/main/tac-talk-guidelines.md)

* CCC-Wide Security Disclosure Process
DM discussed implementing a security disclosure process for the CCC community.

## Annual Project Review: SPDM-Tools 
Yao, Jiewen, presented the annual project review for the SPDM-Tools project.

## CCC LF mentorship: Islet  
Bokdeuk Jeong (BJ) shared the CCC LF mentorship experience.

## Veracruz: 
Derek Miller shared the latest updates for the Veracruz project and the latest progress on its movement to the emeritus state. Discussion ensued. The Chair called for any objections to the motion. Hearing none, it was declared approved by general consent.

##  Live Review GRC Patterns Docs
DM requested feedback on the GRC pattern Documents. Discussion ensued about the open PR and change required before merging.

## Topic Schedule 2025  
* DM reviewed the schedule for the upcoming weeks.

## Any Other Business / Topic Schedule 2025

Topics for the next meeting were discussed and added to the agenda slide.

Next meeting May 29, 2025. The meeting was adjourned by DM at 08:35 am PT
